
1. Добавляем поле image в модель ArticleSpecial:
ALTER TABLE articles_articlespecial ADD COLUMN image VARCHAR(100) NULL AFTER text;
2. Создаем пользователя для pointed:
- на gidinrome:
CREATE USER pointed@141.8.193.148 IDENTIFIED BY "byd738ddu3289eud";
GRANT ALL ON aaveter_0.* TO 'pointed'@'141.8.193.148';
- на rim-gid:
CREATE USER pointed@141.8.193.142 IDENTIFIED BY "byd738ddu3289eud";
GRANT ALL ON aaveter_0.* TO 'pointed'@'141.8.193.142';


- на 10.10.10.7:
CREATE USER pointed@10.10.10.59 IDENTIFIED BY "byd738ddu3289eud";
